00:00:22.556 --> 00:00:23.891
MALE STUDENT: Service
here gets pretty busy.

00:00:23.891 --> 00:00:25.192
You know, we're
all students here;

00:00:25.192 --> 00:00:28.562
we're learning, we're
taking in new experiences so...

00:00:28.562 --> 00:00:31.098
Service can get
pretty crazy and intense.

